743.html|website=The Huffington Post}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Catherine Opie Show at Woodbury University|url=https://placesjournal.org/news/catherine-opie-show-at-woodbury-university/|website=Places Journal}}</ref> |- | June 9 – November 1, 2013 || Pedro E. Guerrero: Photographs of Modern Life<ref>{{cite web|last1=Lange|first1=Alexander|title=Pedro E. Guerrero on Being Inspired by the Masters|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/04/05/garden/questions-for-pedro-guerrero-photographer.html|website=The New York Times}}</ref> |- | October 9 – October 22, 2011 || Richard Barnes: Unnatural Spaces<ref>{{cite web|title=Richard Barnes: Unnatural Spaces|url=http://www.domusweb.it/en/photo-essays/2011/10/03/richard-barnes-unnatural-spaces.html|website=Domus}}</ref> |- | October 2010 || Image.Architecture.Now<ref>{{cite web|last1=Boone|first1=Lisa|title=A Celebration of Julius Shulman|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/home_blog/2010/10/julius-shulman-woodbury.html|website=Los Angeles Times}}</ref> |}
